There are 4 questions in the test

1. how many notes does the major scale has?
The correct answer is: 7 ?

2. what scale is considered the scale of shabat by the jewish religion?
The correct answer is: hijaz ?

3. what kind of scales are used in japanese traditional music?
(1) chromatic scales
(2) heptatonic scales
(3) pentatonic scales
(4) hexatonic scales
(5) None of the answers are correct
(6) More than one answer is correct
The correct answer is:(3) pentatonic scales

4. what is the origin of blues?
(1) african rythms and scales combined with classical instruments
(2) country music combined with classical composition
(3) south american folkore
(4) gypsy music
(5) None of the answers are correct
(6) More than one answer is correct
The correct answer is:(1) african rythms and scales combined with classical instruments


